snippet.textDisplay: F250,,, I miss the 1994 F250HD I sold 6 years ago after my Lyme disease diagnosis. The clutch slave had failed. It had the 300-6, ZF 5 speed and 2 wheel drive,,, wish it had been 4 wheel drive. The buyer parted it out with only 107,000 miles. It was indestructible. I delivered pizza with it through about half of 2010. It sure was fun being one of the few pickups on the road when lots of people were driving little tin can economy cars.
